name":"阿杰","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"阿傑","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"А Цзе","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zhang Jie","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"阿傑是中國內地的男性配音演員、配音導演，本名張傑。\n\n北京圈知名配音演員，729 聲工場的創始人。\n\n聲線華麗，配翩翩佳公子一類的男性角色非常貼合，且有自己的特色。\n\n本科專業是旅遊英語，畢業以後做過一陣子導遊，後發現自己心底裏還是最愛配音，於是走上了配音道路。先是加入網絡社團聲優之翼（現聲創聯盟），後與 X - ray，老房等人成立了網絡配音社團 729 配音組。2006 年開始踏入配音行業。","name":"阿傑","primary":false}}]}},"person_1493969_translations":{"at":1774718573336,"data":{"id":1493969,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Amiah Miller is an American actress and model. She starred in the 2017 film War for the Planet of the Apes. She also appears in the TV series Henry Danger, Best Friends Whenever and MacGyver.","name":"Amiah Miller","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"어마이아 밀러","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"艾米亞·米勒","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"阿米尔·米勒（Amiah Miller）是美国女演员和模特。她出演了 2017 年的电影《人猿星球之战》。她还出现在电视连续剧《Henry Danger》、《Best Friends Wheny》和《MacGyver》中。","name":"阿米尔·米勒","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"آمیا میلر","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","na